TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Present-Value Relation: Tests Based on Implied Variance Bounds
AU  - LeRoy, Stephen F.
AU  - Porter, Richard D.
AB  - [This paper investigates the implications for asset price dispersion of conventional security valuation models. Successively sharper variance bounds on asset prices are derived. Large-sample tests of the bounds are determined and applied to aggregated and disaggregated price and earnings data of U.S. corporations.]
C1  - Full publication date: May, 1981
