TY  - JOUR
TI  - Testing For Unit Roots: 1
AU  - Evans, G. B. A.
AU  - Savin, N. E.
AB  - [This paper investigates the distribution of the least squares estimator of the coefficient α in the model @c"t = @a@c"t -"1 + @?"t where the @?"t where the @?"t are independently distributed N (O, @s^2). The exact finite sample and limiting distributions are calculated when α ≥ 1 and finite sample distributions when α < 1. These distributions are used to compute the power functions of tests of the random walk hypothesis α = 1 as well as the hypotheses.]
